{"tid":1799774,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗暴之戰】中立也容不下 14年佔中送水警被踢出谷","createTime":"2019-12-27T07:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T11:17:33.000Z","uid":75778,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"26f15870a035eb26677cc4305a53c3fc71aada65","tid":1799774,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P1cfr7P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP1cfr7P.jpg&h=a23da214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家應會記得五年前雨傘運動期間，有一名警員進行驅散時將自己的水分給示威者飲用，阿輝說該名警員在今次運動中，曾在Facebook留言指警察不應使用過份武力、應切身處地在示威者立場去想等這些中立的說法，「就夾硬俾人屈佢話『係黃㗎喇，啲WhatsApp group踢走晒佢喇，唔好畀佢喺度攞機密資料喇。』」<br />\n<br />\n我唔敢講佢係黃C定白警<br />\n但見佢呢種type忠忠直直 覺得唔啱就會出聲<br />\n見到popo咁撚顛 相信佢都睇唔過眼<br />\n我覺得佢係呢個大染缸仍能保持獨立思考真係好難得 而佢應該都好撚辛苦<br />\n日撚日比班毅進仔洗腦"},{"pid":"53fbc64d1c2ddb9c42311b155277b49f146d2c33","tid":1799774,"uid":246768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:19:23.000Z","msg":"1229見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ERG7f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ERG7f3.jpg&h=5b4e41b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/negPwHK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnegPwHK.jpg&h=2078beda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0dRv0A5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0dRv0A5.jpg&h=9ac2d4e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RbV442L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbV442L.jpg&h=a96c0e3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7e8e1c0a739545feab7743087d73277654b06cb","tid":1799774,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:22:32.000Z","msg":"白警？"},{"pid":"1a0fb2